{"tid":452260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒地倡蕉坑2000米地換9700米官地","createTime":"2017-10-30T04:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T06:19:14.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b63711fb5fedb78fc33973ba5ec9e610f90a30d8","tid":452260,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171030/s00007/1cf62900f04186b633ffc5d1c0c0e13c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171030%2Fs00007%2F1cf62900f04186b633ffc5d1c0c0e13c.jpg&h=bce6821f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《施政報告》提出以公私營混合模式發展「港人首置上車盤」，多個發展商如恒基地產（恒地）和會德豐都率先和議。前者已成功把屬下的大埔蕉坑地與鄰近官地一併改劃用途，後者則正就擁有的洞梓地申請改劃。本報翻查城規會資料，發現改劃的蕉坑地皮，恒地建議把其擁有、分佈於公營房屋發展土地上的近2000平方米私人地，撥歸政府，以換取9000多平方米官地，讓該公司整合蕉坑地皮上的私人土地，以興建私樓，提供506個單位，另地盤則撥歸政府建289個單位。有立法會議員形容此舉為「蛇吞象」，擔心日後更多地產發展商藉首置計劃名義整合土地發展（見另稿）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171030/s00007/1cf5f656bbffbec980db89e93b5d46bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171030%2Fs00007%2F1cf5f656bbffbec980db89e93b5d46bb.jpg&h=dc3816e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171030/s00007/1cf63f64ac7bd2bbe7c7604b4ab01493.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171030%2Fs00007%2F1cf63f64ac7bd2bbe7c7604b4ab01493.jpg&h=acfa6378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171030/s00002/1509300125827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171030%2Fs00002%2F1509300125827&d=smCtCamarhrpjCAdrbEdar%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=05074e41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171030%2Fs00002%2F1509300125827&h=79c8f1ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171030/s00002/1509300125827</a>"},{"pid":"3971af350d265e3e1b5172d5e9825532de05d688","tid":452260,"uid":61300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"大富翁mode：我用長洲換你山頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bdd8f3c726dbcdfbff601a2e0bab5d28dbeff4","tid":452260,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大富翁mode：我用長洲換你山頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ca3b4ae6f8341b90c67d59030c697b43d67f3a","tid":452260,"uid":48134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"張家輝: 荔枝角+長沙灣 賭 旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}